story_txt:
Hello.I'm Michael. I'm an experienced engineer, product and project manager. I have been working in IT since 2003.I like clever video games and I believe there are millions of clever people who want to play clever games with other people.Snek Fite is a multiplayer game. It's not real-time multiplayer.  You have time to think, to program your battle snake and check how it behaves on battle arena. You program a snake to hunt enemy's tails, avoid dead ends, keep its tail secured.After that, you can run duels with other snakes, run 4-snakes battles and Battle Royale mode (9 snakes on a field). It's what already works.Now I and my small team want to make more possibilities: tournaments with prizes, programming snakes with AI, new design, cooperative mode, clans and lots of other things. And in the future, if everything will be great, we will manufacture a robosnake. But only if the original game will be successful. It's multiplayer. We can't work without clever people. Without you. If you are in intellectual games, love programming (even if you can't), join us. You are an awesome person!Now we need two important things:
you as a player;
your friends as players;
funding, to be able to finish planned incredible must-have game features.
We will spend money on new design, cooperative mode, tournaments and other important things. We will export all battles historical data to the public, so you can use it to teach your neural network if you are in AI. But you don't have to be a programmer to play Snek Fite. Keep it in mind.Here is our roadmap: https://github.com/noff/snek/projects/1 Join our club, get your Snek Hat or Snek T-Shirt and help us to make clever games great again!
